{"tid":687184,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗要5,000萬歐元年薪！唔通曼聯真係接手","createTime":"2018-06-02T04:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T07:31:34.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fc1c9d015b7781c0b911e9e452e522f914ab160f","tid":687184,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"06月02日(六) 09:13   <br />\n<br />\n西班牙《機密報》爆料，皇家馬德里巨星C朗唔滿意主席皮里茲，經常放風想收購巴黎聖日耳門嘅尼馬，而且嫌自己人工低，要求得到除稅後5,000萬歐元新合約，環顧整個球整，相信得曼聯願意為佢開出呢份天價合同咋！ <br />\n<br />\n消息話，C朗希望佢目前嘅除稅後2,100萬歐元年薪，增加到除稅後5,000萬歐元，即係要人工高過美斯同尼馬，不過皇馬考慮到，今季C朗上半程狀態好差，下季踢成點冇人知，所以覺得呢個要求冇辨法接受，假如曼聯真係有興趣，放人絕對唔奇喎！"},{"pid":"b0deb448cba41c61a333a9e4733fecd08781595d","tid":687184,"uid":120715,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:35:05.000Z","msg":"當年賣c朗筆錢都未用完"},{"pid":"c920a6baa561fa1455a2fa2309940134a672434a","tid":687184,"uid":142819,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"33歲 唔扣人工算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3c3601c14b39ef7732b45fffa8a2c5a9018333","tid":687184,"uid":169487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0deb448cba41c61a333a9e4733fecd08781595d","tid":687184,"uid":120715,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:35:05.000Z","msg":"當年賣c朗筆錢都未用完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"買完再賣出去筆錢又可以用多十年"},{"pid":"3fdf6b949128d9a460f15c1b9f0e76c20a027e89","tid":687184,"uid":106675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"當年筆錢買晒700又同你講咩"},{"pid":"17e17fa6bd6eb29d1646269dc2e7266245544343","tid":687184,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:36:56.000Z","msg":"曼聯老人院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d630d73c1f0f05259b1113cbde9c2bce8ae36a3","tid":687184,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:39:43.000Z","